n  Sproutix (SPX) – Whitepaper
1. Executive Summary
Sproutix (SPX) is the native token of the Farming Game, a play-to-earn experience built directly into
Telegram Mini Apps and powered by the TON blockchain.
The mission is simple: gamify farming through mining, growing, and harvesting tokens, while
building a vibrant community that rewards early participation and long-term engagement.
2. Vision & Problem Statement
Play-to-earn gaming has grown significantly, yet most projects face two key challenges:
- Complex onboarding – requiring wallets, external apps, or high entry barriers.
- Unsustainable tokenomics – tokens lose value quickly due to inflationary models.
Farming solves these problems by:
- Running natively on Telegram Mini Apps, accessible to millions instantly.
- Introducing controlled mining mechanics, ensuring balanced token emissions.
- Combining gaming and social experiences to keep users engaged beyond speculation.
3. The Token: Sproutix (SPX)
Sproutix is a fungible token (Jetton standard) on the TON blockchain.
Token Specs:
- Name: Sproutix
- Ticker: SPX
- Blockchain: TON (Jetton Standard TEP-74)
- Total Supply: [to be defined]
- Decimals: 9
Use Cases:
- Rewards for in-game mining & farming.
- Purchase of in-game items, boosts, or upgrades.
- Participation in giveaways, special events, and future governance.
- Liquidity for future DeFi integrations on TON.
4. Game Dynamics
The Farming Game is designed around three simple mechanics:
1. Plant (Start Mining): Users begin farming through daily tasks in the Telegram mini app.
2. Grow (Progress): Mining continues over time, with boosts or upgrades increasing efficiency.
3. Harvest (Rewards): Players collect their mined SPX tokens and use them in-game or trade them.
Future expansions will include leaderboards, PvP challenges, cooperative farming, and seasonal
events.
5. Mining in Telegram Mini App

Mining is interactive, fun, and fair.
- Daily Limits: Users can only mine a certain amount per day, avoiding uncontrolled inflation.
- Task-Based Rewards: Completing missions (clicks, referrals, group participation) grants mining
boosts.
- Progression System: Long-term players benefit from upgrades without making it impossible for
new players to catch up.
6. Ecosystem & Roadmap
Phase 1 – Token Deployment: Deploy Sproutix (SPX) on TON, launch mining functionality.
Phase 2 – Community Growth: Early giveaways and awareness campaigns.
Phase 3 – Token Sale: IDO/IGO and liquidity on TON DEXs.
Phase 4 – Game Expansion: Items, upgrades, PvP, seasonal events.
Phase 5 – Long-Term Growth: Governance and ecosystem partnerships.
7. Tokenomics & Distribution
Proposed allocation:
- 40% – Mining Rewards
- 20% – Public Sale & Liquidity
- 15% – Community & Giveaways
- 15% – Team & Development
- 10% – Marketing & Partnerships
8. Sustainability Model
The Farming ecosystem is built for long-term value:
- Mining is capped daily to prevent hyperinflation.
- Token sinks (items, upgrades, events) encourage continuous usage.
- Giveaways and rewards attract new users while balancing supply.
9. Team & Community
The Sproutix team focuses on crypto accessibility and gaming innovation. Telegram + TON ensures
anyone can start farming in seconds.
Community-driven growth:
- Active Telegram groups
- Events & giveaways
- Future governance through token-holder voting
10. Conclusion
Sproutix (SPX) and the Farming Game represent the future of casual play-to-earn gaming on TON.
By combining mining mechanics, community growth, and sustainable tokenomics, we are planting
the seeds for a long-term, engaging ecosystem.
